item.title: Rain Theif
item.author: jsacosta1103@gmail.com (Jerad Acosta)
item.description: Look Around; Look Around I do not see you; You do not see myself Now look around who do you see? This is a person now using me! Stare into their brow Study them down. Gulp the static space between yourself and this imposter. Cold and tight as the environment around compresses unto a point. Flashpoint. Erupt. Soul beaming.
